nodes.text: Sector 33. B-881 was a subsector located in the Lothal sector of the galaxy's Outer Rim Territories. During the age of the Galactic Empire, the Lothal sector, including Sector 33. B-881, was ruled by the Empire and governed by Arihnda Pryce, a human female, a Lothal native, as well as Moff Stattata.
